<tr>
<th style=";;" colspan="2" class="navbox-title">
<div style="float:left; width:6em;text-align:left;">&#160;</div>
<span style="font-size:100%;">General principles</span></th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<div>
<p><i>Article 1: <a href="/wiki/Freedom_(philosophy)" title="Freedom (philosophy)">Freedom</a>, <a href="/wiki/Egalitarianism" title="Egalitarianism">Egalitarianism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Dignity" title="Dignity">Dignity</a> and <a href="/wiki/Brother" title="Brother" class="mw-redirect">Brotherhood</a></i><br />
<i>Article 2: <a href="/wiki/Universal_ethic" title="Universal ethic" class="mw-redirect">Universality of rights</a></i></p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
